{"id": 1260, "genre": 1001, "title": "你无法辞职的理由是什么？", "description": "辞职的理由无非工资不合适，团队不和谐之类，可那些喊着要死了要死了但还不跳槽的人是为啥呢？（题图来自：AQ studio）", "record_count": 4657, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161008180526rVgU4phOI2eTw0fB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-27T03:00:33Z", "options": [{"id": 127671, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 340, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599488}, {"id": 121943, "content": "年终奖还妹发呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 781, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 127661, "content": "户口#￥……&f￥%u￥！c！k*@", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273667}, {"id": 121940, "content": "一说要换工作爸妈就苦口婆心：赶快定下来别折腾了，你都没对象还敢没工作？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 100, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 121941, "content": "我的工种只有这个单位有，换了不知道该干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 121942, "content": "我的工种只有这个城市有，即使换了工作也无法换个更宜居的城市生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 127652, "content": "谁知道下一个是不是更坑呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 499, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145747}, {"id": 127653, "content": " 工作这么久依然是月光族，辞职后连再找工作至上岗期间的成本都不够···", "image": null, "praise_count": 446, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349071}, {"id": 127654, "content": "还没有做好准备", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811038}, {"id": 127655, "content": "再跑路的话简历就一片疮痍了", "image": null, "praise_count": 149, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141318}, {"id": 127656, "content": "现在的公司我看不上，换工作别的公司看不上我", "image": null, "praise_count": 408, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143082}, {"id": 127657, "content": "换工作的成本太高。", "image": null, "praise_count": 120, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810471}, {"id": 127658, "content": "还没有找好下家，现在走了，万一长时间找不到就惨了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701169}, {"id": 127659, "content": "厌倦了现在的工作，想换个城市和行业，但还没找到喜欢的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647418}, {"id": 127660, "content": "害怕，走不出舒适区。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 267, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810209}, {"id": 127662, "content": "还没有?下定决心，哪里好像都一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 477475}, {"id": 127663, "content": "刚辞职，无所畏惧，嘻嘻", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113515}, {"id": 127664, "content": "没有勇气面对陌生的环境", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 282055}, {"id": 127665, "content": "创业中...", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527389}, {"id": 127666, "content": "眼高手低腿残", "image": null, "praise_count": 177, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669206}, {"id": 127667, "content": "房租啊信用卡啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662367}, {"id": 127668, "content": "总担心没钱生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751188}, {"id": 127669, "content": "刚毕业一年多，什么都没学到，辞职凭什么在找工作???", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 767704}, {"id": 127670, "content": "全公司就我没奖金  干嘛不辞职", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811075}, {"id": 127674, "content": "新工作会换城市，要换房子，要找新的交通方式，要熟悉新的生活环境……好累啊눈_눈", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699925}, {"id": 127675, "content": "感恩\n感谢公司，感谢同事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723000}, {"id": 127676, "content": "工资待遇好", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803948}, {"id": 127677, "content": "早上刚提了离职，结果老板一挽留之前的决心就没了，大概还是觉得年底了吧…", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811088}, {"id": 127678, "content": "暂时还没有找到更好的下家，还有今年经济放缓的影响吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723030}, {"id": 127679, "content": "暂时还没有找到更好的下家，还有今年经济放缓的影响吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723030}, {"id": 127680, "content": "暂时还没有找到更好的下家，还有今年经济放缓的影响吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723030}, {"id": 127681, "content": "暂时还没有找到更好的下家，还有今年经济放缓的影响吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723030}, {"id": 127744, "content": "懒得换，将就着干吧，谁知道下一个会是啥样，没准更让人糟心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 356559}, {"id": 128768, "content": "不知道还能干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651023}, {"id": 127745, "content": "想做的工作能力不足，能做的工作又没现在的好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802200}, {"id": 128001, "content": "因为婆婆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597485}, {"id": 127746, "content": "难道就没有一个和我一样因为责任心的吗！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811272}, {"id": 127747, "content": "不知道下一个工作看不看得上我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679602}, {"id": 128003, "content": "到新的环境认识陌生的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 812132}, {"id": 128004, "content": "每个月家庭开销3-4万块 现在城市很难找到工资这么高的工作了 没勇气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 812155}, {"id": 128005, "content": "还有上升空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802176}, {"id": 127750, "content": "感觉又要重新来过啊 还没完全做好准备和储备好足够的勇气", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808640}, {"id": 128006, "content": "第一份工作是为了立足社会，目前单腿站，工作中没有主动学习过本职外的知识技能，导致不具备第二份工作需要的从业能力，人活27，脑袋突然开光，于是穷追猛赶，唯怕缺少毅力，在此与各君共勉，祝成功。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810969}, {"id": 127752, "content": "老板不放我走", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91804}, {"id": 127753, "content": "努力了，还没收获，不甘心！就算困难，也要按照自己的节奏一步步走。", "image": "img/option/option/20161027150608frLYnZ2RlHWIa1hp.jpg", "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811290}, {"id": 127754, "content": "懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262968}, {"id": 129034, "content": "和女盆友一个单位", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814751}, {"id": 127755, "content": "没什么拿出手的技术。就原地踏步了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800047}, {"id": 128011, "content": "因为还没有工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809289}, {"id": 127756, "content": "还没攒够，可以出去不工作3个月的资本、、、", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 86691}]}